            "text": "Here are some of the top-rated places for facials in Katy, TX, based on customer reviews and services offered:\n\n*   **SkinSpirit Katy** is a medical spa in the LaCenterra at Cinco Ranch shopping mall that offers custom and signature facials tailored to your skin's needs. They focus on providing quality experiences and results, with online scheduling for convenience.\n*   **Anita's Skin Care Clinic** offers a variety of customized facials and skincare services, taking a holistic approach to address individual skin concerns. They specialize in holistic skincare and beauty therapy treatments in Cinco Ranch.\n*   **Divinity Spa** provides customized facial treatments using techniques like radiofrequency, ultrasound, and illuminator.\n*   **Spavia Cinco Ranch** offers a luxurious spa experience with customized facials and resort-like amenities. They also offer specialized treatments like the Sculpt & Lift Facial and the Platinum Ice and Glow Facial.\n*   **MedSpa at Villagio** is a medical spa that offers a range of services, including facials, laser hair removal, and other treatments for skin rejuvenation. They have been awarded by Image Skincare as Medspa of the Year twice.\n*   **Katy Med Tech Spa** is known for its dedication to customer service and personalized treatments. They offer first-time customer deals on their Ageless Signature Facial and Body Treatments.\n*   **Katy Medi Spa** provides advanced skincare treatments, including facials, chemical peels, and skin resurfacing, in a comfortable spa environment.\n*   **Face to Face Spa** offers a variety of facials, including classic facials and Hydrafacials, with options for more specialized treatments like chemical peels and microneedling. They also have a premium medi-facial for first-time clients.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa Katy** combines the relaxation of a traditional spa with medical-grade treatments.\n*   **Luxe Medical Aesthetics** provides customized facials and has received positive feedback for their estheticians and the glowing results clients experience.\n*   **All Is Well Massage & Spa** offers a calming atmosphere and top-notch services, with a focus on wellness and relaxation.\n\n"
          }
